# 🔥 Keywords vs Identifiers

| Keywords          | Identifiers           |
| ----------------- | --------------------- |
| Reserved words    | User-defined names    |
| Cannot be changed | Can be changed        |
| Part of syntax    | Created by programmer |

---

# 🔥 Variables vs Keywords

| Variables    | Keywords         |
| ------------ | ---------------- |
| Store data   | Reserved words   |
| Can change   | Fixed meanings   |
| User-defined | Language-defined |

